textBeforeTable: Here's a summary of some of the announced retail GTX 570 cards available and how they stack up: The new GeForce GTX 570 is the latest addition to NVIDIA's GTX 500 series of DirectX 11 (DX11) GPUs designed for PC gaming enthusiast platforms. With support for NVIDIA 3D Vision and NVIDIA Surround technologies, it brings faster and quieter performance without compromising on the graphics. NVIDIA's SLI technology also allows gaming performance to be heightened by adding a second GeForce GTX 570 to the system. With these features and more, the GTX 570 ensures the best gaming experience.
